\v 1 \add This letter is from\add* Paul, a slaveВҰ139882 of God and a missionary of \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ139888\nd* and follower of the faithВҰ139890 of the ones thatВҰ139896 God has chosen.
