\v 4 \x + \xo 1:4: \xt 2Cor 8:23; Gal 2:3; 2Tim 4:10.\x*To TitosВҰ139929, my true son due to our commonВҰ139933 faithВҰ139934. May \nd GodВҰ139940\nd* the fatherВҰ139941 and our saviourВҰ139948 \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ139944\nd* give you graceВҰ139935 and peaceВҰ139938.
\s1 Qualifications for leaders
