\v 11 This is becauseВҰ140280 God's graceВҰ140282 which offers salvationВҰ140286 to all peopleВҰ140289 has appearedВҰ140279
\v 12 and teaches us that when we distance ourselves from ungodlinessВҰ140297 and worldlyВҰ140300 lustsВҰ140301, we can liveВҰ140307 sensiblyВҰ140302 and justlyВҰ140304 and devoutlyВҰ140306 in the presentВҰ140310 age.
\v 13 Then we can look forward to the blessingВҰ140314 of the \add вүҲmajestic appearanceВҰ140317\add* of ourВҰ140325 greatВҰ140321 \nd GodВҰ140322\nd* and saviourВҰ140324, \nd Yeshua\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ140328\nd*
\v 14 \x + \xo 2:14: a \xt Psa 130:8; \xo b \xt Exo 19:5; Deu 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; 1Pe 2:9.\x*who gaveВҰ140330 himself for us in orderВҰ140335 to redeemВҰ140336 us from all lawlessnessВҰ140340 and to purifyВҰ140342 us into his chosenВҰ140345 peopleВҰ140344, eager to do goodВҰ140347 things.
\p
\v 15 Teach theseВҰ140349 things as you encourage some and scold others, butВҰ140352 don't let anyoneВҰ140359 disrespectВҰ140361 you.
\c 3
\s1 Expected behaviour
