\p
\v 1 Remind people to conform to their rulersВҰ140365 and authoritiesВҰ140367, beingВҰ140368 obedient and readyВҰ140376 to do anything that's goodВҰ140374.
\v 2 Don't slanderВҰ140379 others, be peaceableВҰ140380. Don't be strong-willed, but rather show gentlenessВҰ140382 to all peopleВҰ140391.
\v 3 We were also foolishВҰ140397 and stubborn at one time, strayingВҰ140399 from the good and giving in to variousВҰ140405 lustsВҰ140402 and pleasures, beingВҰ140399 mean and envious, even full of hate and hatingВҰ140412 one anotherВҰ140413.
\v 4 ButВҰ140418 when \nd GodВҰ140425\nd* ourВҰ140424 saviourВҰ140423 revealed his kindnessВҰ140417 andВҰ140418 loveВҰ140420 for humankind,
\v 5 he savedВҰ140443 us, not because of the вҖҳgood deedsвҖҷ thatВҰ140429 we did, butВҰ140449 out of his mercyВҰ140441. He regeneratedВҰ140448 us throughВҰ140445 washingВҰ140447 and renewedВҰ140450 us by \add his\add* holy \nd spiritВҰ140451\nd*
\v 6 which he lavishly pouredВҰ140454 on us throughВҰ140458 \nd YeshuaВҰ140459\nd* the \nd messiahВҰ140460\nd*
\v 7 so that we might becomeВҰ140472 heirsВҰ140470 with the expectation of living forever, havingВҰ140465 been declared that we have no outstanding legal charges thanks to his graceВҰ140469.
\v 8 That statement can be trusted. I want you to confirmВҰ140485 those things so that those who have believedВҰ140492 in \nd GodВҰ140494\nd* will be leadingВҰ140490 in wanting to do good things. TheseВҰ140495 things are good and benefitВҰ140500 everyoneВҰ140502.
\rem /s1 Paul's Final Remarks and Greetings; Final instructions
