\v 9 ButВҰ140506 avoidВҰ140514 foolishВҰ140503 debatesВҰ140505, arguments about ancestry, other strifeВҰ140509, and quarrelsВҰ140512 about \add God's\add* commands because theyВҰ140515 all achieve nothing and waste time.
