\v 12 \x + \xo 3:12: \xt Acts 20:4; Eph 6:21-22; Col 4:7-8; 2Tim 4:12.\x*WheneverВҰ140537 I sendВҰ140538 ArtemasВҰ140539 or TychicusВҰ140543 to you, you should try to meet me at NicopolisВҰ140549, becauseВҰ140551 I'veВҰ140552 decided to spend the winterВҰ140553 thereВҰ140550.
