\v 14 Our peopleВҰ140571 must also be learningВҰ140567 to be leadingВҰ140574 in doing goodВҰ140572 things to meet the necessaryВҰ140577 needsВҰ140578 so that theyВҰ140581 won'tВҰ140580 be unproductive.
